ly newsletter by David Pierce designed to tell you everything you need to download, watch, read, listen to, and explore that fits in The Verge’s universe.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/form\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/article\u003e\u003c/main\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
